==English==

===Proper Noun===
# [[country pop|Pop-styled]] [[country music]] which became popular during the early 1980s, following the release of the 1980 movie "Urban Cowboy."
# The title of a 1980 [[movie]] starring John Travolta and Debra Winger.

===Etymology===
The term is borrowed from the title of a popular 1980 movie starring John Travolta and Debra Winger and featuring several country music performances.